{
  "title":"Violence is Wrong",
  "date":"2011-10-10 CST",
  "origin":"Funny Logic",
  "url":"text-violence-is-wrong",
  "author":"Ryan X. Charles"
}




<p>&#8220;You should never be violent,&#8221; she said.</p>

<p>&#8220;What if someone disagrees with you?&#8221; he said.</p>

<p>&#8220;Then you should constrain them, pull their pants down, and spank them until they agree,&#8221; she said.</p>

<p>&#8220;That sounds violent,&#8221; he said.</p>

<p>&#8220;Unfortunately, it&#8217;s the only way some people listen,&#8221; she said.</p>

<p>He did some calculations in his head.</p>

<p>&#8220;I disagree with you,&#8221; he said.</p>

<p>They began to make out soon thereafter.</p>

